Retailer Game has published the third in a series of deals as part of its month-long Black Friday 2020 sale. These deals are valid between 18 November – 24 November and include sales on a variety of electronic and home items. The retailer is offering Black Friday specials throughout November, with new specials becoming available each week. The weekly schedule for Game’s Black Friday deals is as follows: Week 1: runs 2-10 November (ended)
Week 2: runs 11-17 November (ending)
Week 3: runs 18-24 November (next)
Week 4: runs 25-29 November (coming) “We have undertaken negotiation with all our suppliers to ensure we are able to offer our shoppers the unbeatable deals they have come to expect from Game on Black Friday,” said Andrew Stein, vice president of Game. “While we have ensured all our stores are well-stocked, we encourage all our customers to take advantage of these deals as soon as possible to avoid disappointment.” During the Black Friday 2020 sale, Game stores will follow the operating hours below: Monday to Friday: 09:00 – 18:00
Saturday: 09:00 – 17:00
Sunday and Public Holidays: 09:00 – 16:00 The latest Game Black Friday specials will be available from Wednesday 18 November. You can find the full list of deals below. <img class="size-full wp-image-449323 aligncenter" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Game-Deals3.jpg" alt="Game Deals" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Game-Deals3.jpg 640w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Game-Deals3-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="size-full wp-image-449325 aligncenter" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Game-Deals4.jpg" alt="Game Deals" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Game-Deals4.jpg 640w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Game-Deals4-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="size-full wp-image-449337 aligncenter" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Game-Deal-11.jpg" alt="Game Deal" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Game-Deal-11.jpg 640w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Game-Deal-11-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="size-full wp-image-449329 aligncenter" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Game-Deals6.jpg" alt="Game Deals" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Game-Deals6.jpg 640w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Game-Deals6-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width